## Limitations

This analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the inherent biases present in opinion-based sources. Additionally, the effectiveness of homeschooling versus public schooling can vary significantly based on individual circumstances, such as the quality of the homeschooling curriculum and the resources available in public schools. Further empirical research is needed to draw more definitive conclusions.